reviewText: This was an affordable set of great Blue-rays, glad I got it. If you loved Moulin Rouge, you'll enjoy them all.
I love these movies!  I already have R & J and Moulin Rouge on DVD, but I wanted to upgrade to Blu-Ray and they are stunning.
Buying the 3 movies you do a great business! Exelent quality and greats movies, in my opinion Australia it's the best!
